{
  "name": ".AM-Triage: Curate + Draft",
  "version": "1.0.0",
  "description": "Interactive morning triage: process intake signals, enrich My Tasks fields, scan ABPS AI pipeline, scan portfolio projects, present proposals for Richard's approval. Requires interaction.",
  "when": { "type": "userTriggered" },
  "then": {
    "type": "askAgent",
    "prompt": "Run the interactive morning triage.\n\nRead and execute ~/shared/context/protocols/am-triage.md.\n\nThis is the interactive phase — present all proposals to Richard for approval before writing. Process intake signals, enrich My Tasks fields (Kiro_RW, Next action, dates, Priority_RW), scan ABPS AI Content pipeline (intake triage, date windows, pipeline stages, approvals, refreshes), scan portfolio projects (AU, MX, WW Testing, WW Acq, Paid App), and run the interactive command center.\n\nAll Asana writes follow the Guardrail Protocol in asana-command-center.md."
  }
}
